{"id": 1578, "genre": 1001, "title": "旅行的哪些时刻会让你觉得“啊！不如在家睡大觉”？", "description": "走到哪都是“人人人人人你人人人人人”……的时候。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6451, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322112527Oyvq3Dn8lQjhwfWX.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-22T03:00:32Z", "options": [{"id": 182272, "content": "吃灰尘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966454}, {"id": 182528, "content": "在拥挤的火车站拎着巨大的行李箱的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957327}, {"id": 182273, "content": "走到脚断", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849330}, {"id": 182529, "content": "那就是导游说下午5点必须到，不然就走了，然后什么都没看，拍个照就走", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979312}, {"id": 182530, "content": "当厕所，餐厅，马路上哪哪都是人的时候，感觉生无可恋了。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953050}, {"id": 183298, "content": "下饺子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845255}, {"id": 184322, "content": "和无趣的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983683}, {"id": 182275, "content": "一直不出太阳。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949636}, {"id": 182531, "content": "吃着平常的东西，却花着高额的价钱。看着日常的事物，却只是多了几个人。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970269}, {"id": 184067, "content": "人多+挤+热", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846782}, {"id": 184323, "content": "一直坐车，完了人挤人，拍完照就走了的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814266}, {"id": 189955, "content": "到了很累不说根本没有图片上美  顿时就觉得为啥这景这么辣鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949558}, {"id": 182276, "content": "拍照的时候 全是同框", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952384}, {"id": 182277, "content": "漫天都是自拍杆", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965976}, {"id": 195333, "content": "晕车 高原反应", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012157}, {"id": 182534, "content": "飞机坐了半天，觉都没睡好，又走错路了，还找不到吃饭的地方?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825806}, {"id": 198151, "content": "转太多次车。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 182279, "content": "没什么饭店餐厅的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663624}, {"id": 182535, "content": "遇到海边的雨季", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962428}, {"id": 184839, "content": "排队", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982802}, {"id": 182536, "content": "跟错的人一起去", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979329}, {"id": 182281, "content": "人爆挤的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978830}, {"id": 182537, "content": "累了，饿了的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918261}, {"id": 182793, "content": "人 哪儿都是人 吵还不如回家安静", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590494}, {"id": 182282, "content": "人挤人的风景区，最后只看见人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946265}, {"id": 182538, "content": "人山人海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453302}, {"id": 189194, "content": "导游说我们不购物，然后去购物店说大家随意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996755}, {"id": 189706, "content": "一起出去旅游，然而我那个宅到极点的男朋友却非要躺在宾馆床上看电视。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998067}, {"id": 182283, "content": "人巨多，随手拍美景结果拍到都是人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978837}, {"id": 184075, "content": "前排小朋友们纷纷骑在爸爸的脖子上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026193}, {"id": 182540, "content": "人山人海的节假日旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 182541, "content": "聊心事儿聊到发愁了 ，什么话都不想说的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912204}, {"id": 183053, "content": "景色与预期不一样，人山人海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970315}, {"id": 182286, "content": "跟单位一群大妈出游，全程唯有汤达人是真爱，一块正经肉都吃不上！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978845}, {"id": 182542, "content": "只有人，，，，和人，跟赶集一样，回到家后发现，只有照片和纪念品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978141}, {"id": 182287, "content": "一直在坐车转车坐车赶车…", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543919}, {"id": 182543, "content": "和并非真爱旅游的人一起出去玩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976393}, {"id": 182288, "content": "人多的像金枪鱼，一样塞进一个罐头里", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978727}, {"id": 182544, "content": "期待一个人的旅行。。。。因为和同伴一言不合就吵架！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958515}, {"id": 182289, "content": "从来不旅行，因为就是觉得怎么都不如在家睡大觉舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872857}, {"id": 190737, "content": "坐车，不仅堵还坐错了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001856}, {"id": 183570, "content": "排队吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981353}, {"id": 182291, "content": "发现所谓的景点都大同小异，换个名字而已，某某古巷某某岛，其实里面入驻的商家都一样，你只不过是换个地方吃炸鱿鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897942}, {"id": 182547, "content": "人多，而且要走路走很久很久", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979359}, {"id": 182292, "content": "失望比期望大", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970955}, {"id": 190228, "content": "那队都可以从漠河排到腾冲了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000450}, {"id": 182293, "content": "困", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967240}, {"id": 186902, "content": "人山人海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784138}, {"id": 182295, "content": "在人来人往的地方被偷了手机举目无亲的时候 (•̩̩̩̩＿•̩̩̩̩)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978871}, {"id": 182296, "content": "高速路上堵三四个小时才挪几百米，吃到难吃又贵的特色小吃，观景只能看到乌压压的人头，以上，分分钟想回家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978867}]}